page_content: The page provides information on a Volksabstimmung (public vote) held on November 28, 2021, in the canton of Obwalden, Switzerland.
The page is about the Support & IT department of the Obwalden Tax Administration, offering software solutions for electronic tax declarations.
The page offers a downloadable PDF guide for using an online portal related to tax reassessment.
The page offers a downloadable PDF guide for exporting E-Balance CH from ABACUS software for import into CleverTax.
The page provides information on electronic tax declaration solutions, eTax OW for individuals and Obwalden Tax for legal entities, offered by the canton of Obwalden.
The page offers a downloadable PDF titled "IBB-Wegleitung SODK Ost+ 2019," but the content and purpose are not specified.
The page provides information on labor laws and youth protection during vocational training, including downloadable brochures.
